PN,43201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779981070
OL,3,CFatal and serious collisions in Devon
OL,4,Cand Cornwall at lowest level in a
OL,5,Cdecade
OL,7,FThe number of people killed or
OL,8,Fseriously injured on Devon and
OL,9,FCornwall's roads has dropped to the
OL,10,Flowest level in 10 years, new figures
OL,11,Fshow.
OL,13,FProvisional figures from the
OL,14,FDepartment for Transport (DfT) show
OL,15,Fthat in 2025, 48 people were killed
OL,16,Fand 495 seriously injured in
OL,17,Fcollisions in the region.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779981070
OL,3,CFatal and serious collisions in Devon
OL,4,Cand Cornwall at lowest level in a
OL,5,Cdecade
OL,7,FThis is the lowest number since modern
OL,8,Frecording systems were introduced and
OL,9,Falmost 20% lower than the figure for
OL,10,F2024.
OL,12,FThe data also shows that the number of
OL,13,Fkilled or seriously injured (KSI) in
OL,14,Fcollisions has decreased every year
OL,15,Fsince 2022.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779981070
OL,3,CFatal and serious collisions in Devon
OL,4,Cand Cornwall at lowest level in a
OL,5,Cdecade
OL,7,FThe release of the figures comes at
OL,8,Fthe same time as the fifth anniversary
OL,9,Fof the Vision Zero South West road
OL,10,Fsafety partnership, a collaboration
OL,11,Fbetween 17 organisations across the
OL,12,Fregion.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779981070
OL,3,CFatal and serious collisions in Devon
OL,4,Cand Cornwall at lowest level in a
OL,5,Cdecade
OL,7,FThe partnership includes Devon &
OL,8,FCornwall Police, Devon and Somerset
OL,9,FFire and Rescue Service, Cornwall Fire
OL,10,Fand Rescue Service, South Western
OL,11,FAmbulance Service Trust, local
OL,12,Fauthorities, NHS Trusts, air ambulance
OL,13,Fcharities, National Highways and the
OL,14,FOffice of the Police and Crime
OL,15,FCommissioner.
OL,17,FVision Zero South West has committed
OL,18,Fto reducing fatal and serious
OL,19,Fcollisions by 50% by 2030.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779981070
OL,3,CFatal and serious collisions in Devon
OL,4,Cand Cornwall at lowest level in a
OL,5,Cdecade
OL,7,FSergeant Owen Messenger, from Devon &
OL,8,FCornwall Police's road casualty
OL,9,Freduction team told ITV West Country
OL,10,Fthat a large part of their work
OL,11,Finvolves changing people's "mindset so
OL,12,Fthat they drive safer".
OL,14,FHe said: "We do a lot of social media
OL,15,Fwork. We started off by trying to
OL,16,Fengage with young drivers. Young
OL,17,Fdrivers are overrepresented in
OL,18,Fcollision statistics and they're
OL,19,Ftraditionally very, very difficult for
OL,20,Fthe police to reach.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779981070
OL,3,CFatal and serious collisions in Devon
OL,4,Cand Cornwall at lowest level in a
OL,5,Cdecade
OL,7,F"So I worked with a local YouTuber and
OL,8,Fwe started off just doing a couple of
OL,9,Fvideos, and six years later, with two
OL,10,Fmillion followers, we now get around
OL,11,F30 million views a month across the
OL,12,Fsocial media platforms."
OL,14,FHe added: "The cars can get much, much
OL,15,Fsafer but you've still got that driver
OL,16,Fthat is in charge of the car and that
OL,17,Fperson that is behind the wheel. That
OL,18,Fperson is making those decisions and
OL,19,Fit's those decisions that could be
OL,20,Flife or death for other people or
OL,21,Fthemselves on the road."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779981070
OL,3,CFatal and serious collisions in Devon
OL,4,Cand Cornwall at lowest level in a
OL,5,Cdecade
OL,7,FVision Zero South West is funded by
OL,8,Fthe additional costs recovered by
OL,9,FDevon & Cornwall Police from offending
OL,10,Fmotorists through driver training
OL,11,Fschemes and costs awarded by
OL,12,FMagistrates Courts, once the police
OL,13,Foperating costs are met.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779981070
OL,3,CFatal and serious collisions in Devon
OL,4,Cand Cornwall at lowest level in a
OL,5,Cdecade
OL,7,FThe partnership has funded road safety
OL,8,Finitiatives like a motorcycle
OL,9,Fsimulator to train young riders in
OL,10,Fhazard prediction, a UK-first trial of
OL,11,FAI cameras which detect seatbelt and
OL,12,Fmobile phone offences, and more than
OL,13,F#250,000 of community-led safety
OL,14,Fschemes.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779981070
OL,3,CFatal and serious collisions in Devon
OL,4,Cand Cornwall at lowest level in a
OL,5,Cdecade
OL,7,FVision Zero has also funded IMPACT -
OL,8,FThe Centre for Post-Collision
OL,9,FResearch, Innovation and Translation -
OL,10,Fwhich has carried out research that
OL,11,FTania Martin, Joint Operations
OL,12,FDirector at Devon Air Ambulance, has
OL,13,Fpraised as "phenomenal".
OL,15,FShe said that the initial response to
OL,16,Fan accident is "absolutely critical"
OL,17,Ffor patients, and that IMPACT has
OL,18,Fresearched and questioned historical
OL,19,Fadvice such as maintaining the spinal
OL,20,Fcord of people in the vehicle.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779981070
OL,3,CFatal and serious collisions in Devon
OL,4,Cand Cornwall at lowest level in a
OL,5,Cdecade
OL,7,FShe explained: "In most cases, just
OL,8,Fgetting that person out of that
OL,9,Fvehicle, getting them to medical help,
OL,10,Fand getting them to hospital quicker
OL,11,Fcan have a significant impact on their
OL,12,Foutcome and their mortality."
OL,14,FAlison Hernandez, the Police & Crime
OL,15,FCommissioner for Devon, Cornwall and
OL,16,Fthe Isles of Scilly, is chair of
OL,17,FVision Zero South West and said there
OL,18,Fis still "a lot of work to do".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779981070
OL,3,CFatal and serious collisions in Devon
OL,4,Cand Cornwall at lowest level in a
OL,5,Cdecade
OL,7,FShe explained: "We must never forget
OL,8,Fwhat these numbers represent. These
OL,9,Fare real people killed in tragic and
OL,10,Ftraumatic circumstances - loved ones
OL,11,Fand family members, parents and
OL,12,Fchildren, brothers, sisters and
OL,13,Ffriends.
OL,15,F"This is why road safety has always
OL,16,Fbeen a personal priority since I took
OL,17,Foffice in 2016 - and why I helped set
OL,18,Fup the Vision Zero South West
OL,19,Fpartnership."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779981070
OL,3,CFatal and serious collisions in Devon
OL,4,Cand Cornwall at lowest level in a
OL,5,Cdecade
OL,7,FShe added: "We have worked tirelessly
OL,8,Ftowards reducing these figures. This
OL,9,Fhas involved embracing innovation and
OL,10,Ftechnology, being bold and trying new
OL,11,Fthings, being relentless with our
OL,12,Fsafety messaging and campaigns, and
OL,13,Finvesting in things we know make a
OL,14,Fdifference.
OL,16,F"Working in partnership has been
OL,17,Fabsolutely key to every success we've
OL,18,Fhad and I look forward to continuing
OL,19,Fthis work with our partners in the
OL,20,Ffuture."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779981070
OL,3,CFatal and serious collisions in Devon
OL,4,Cand Cornwall at lowest level in a
OL,5,Cdecade
OL,7,FAdrian Leisk, Head of Road Safety for
OL,8,FDevon & Cornwall Police said: "This
OL,9,Fvery welcome news demonstrates the
OL,10,Feffectiveness of the partnership
OL,11,Fapproach to reducing the number of
OL,12,Fpeople killed or seriously injured on
OL,13,Four roads.
OL,15,F"This also reduces the attendant
OL,16,Ftrauma that it causes to the families
OL,17,Fand friends of victims and also helps
OL,18,Fto reduce the massive disruption that
OL,19,Fthe aftermath of serious collision
OL,20,Fcauses to transport, business, and
OL,21,Findividuals.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779981070
OL,3,CFatal and serious collisions in Devon
OL,4,Cand Cornwall at lowest level in a
OL,5,Cdecade
OL,7,F"Whilst this reduction is encouraging,
OL,8,Four thoughts very much remain with
OL,9,Fthose who have lost loved ones in a
OL,10,Froad traffic collision.
OL,12,F"Devon & Cornwall Police officers work
OL,13,Ftirelessly year-round to enforce the
OL,14,Flaws that are there to keep all road
OL,15,Fusers safe.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779981070
OL,3,CFatal and serious collisions in Devon
OL,4,Cand Cornwall at lowest level in a
OL,5,Cdecade
OL,7,F"We are beginning to see that
OL,8,Fenforcement, notably around excessive
OL,9,Fspeed, mobile phone, and seat belt
OL,10,Foffences, and in tandem with lowered
OL,11,Fspeed limits and safety camera
OL,12,Finstallation, is beginning to have a
OL,13,Fmeasurable effect on improving safety
OL,14,Fon our counties' roads."
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/15
